title: D+D Real Czech Challenge
text: The D+D Real Czech Challenge is a <a href="golf">golf</a> tournament on the <a href="Challenge%20Tour">Challenge Tour</a> played in the <a href="Czech%20Republic">Czech Republic</a>. From 2012 to 2018, and from 2021 it was played at the Golf&Spa Kunětická Hora in <a href="D%C5%99%C3%ADte%C4%8D">Dříteč</a>. It moved to the Kaskáda Golf Resort, near <a href="Ku%C5%99im">Kuřim</a>, in 2019.
